{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">知道磁体的两个磁极；掌握磁铁周围磁场的方向。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">磁体周围存在磁场。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">条形磁铁、蹄形磁铁、小磁针</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.将小磁针放在条形磁铁的周围，观察小磁针的偏转方向；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.将小磁针放在蹄形磁铁的周围，观察小磁针的偏转方向。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在磁体外部磁感线是从</span>N<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">极出发回到</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">S</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">极。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">为了方便、形象的描绘磁场，用带箭头的曲线将磁场画出来，这样的曲线叫做磁感线；磁场是真实存在的，磁感线是不存在的。</span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}